[b]Step 5:[/b]

Now search for (still in client.java):

[code]sendMessage("You do not have enough special energy left.");[/code]

And you will see something like this:

[code]if (playerEquipment[playerWeapon] == 8002 && specialAmount <= 25) { // dclaw
specialDamage = 0;
specialDamage2 = 0;
sendMessage("You do not have enough special energy left.");
}
